| **Enable MFA** | If using Azure AD or other identity providers, enforce MFA for RDP logins. | Prevents credential‑only attacks. |
| **Audit & Monitor** | Enable Windows Event Log for RDP (4624, 4625, 4776, 4778, 4779) and forward to a SIEM or CloudWatch. | Detects brute‑force or anomalous activity. |

