| **Network Segmentation** | Place sensitive workloads in isolated subnets; use security groups to restrict egress. | Limits the attack surface. |
| **Data Loss Prevention (DLP)** | Use AWS Macie or third‑party DLP to scan S3 objects. | Detects sensitive data before it leaves. |
| **Logging & Alerting** | CloudWatch metric filters for `PutObject`; SNS alerts. | Immediate visibility. |
| **Regular Audits** | AWS Config rules (`s3-bucket-public-read-prohibited`, `s3-bucket-public-write-prohibited`). | Continuous compliance. |

